Attribution Notes
-----------------
- Lexical source material is edited by Þórdís Úlfarsdóttir and Halldóra
  Jónsdóttir (dataset authors of record for the 2026-02 ISLEX release used
  here), published by Stofnun Árna Magnússonar í íslenskum fræðum, in
  collaboration with the ISLEX Nordic partner institutions in Denmark,
  Norway, Sweden, the Faroe Islands and Finland, via the CLARIN Iceland
  repository.
- See CREDITS.md for the full citation, the complete list of participating
  institutions per country, additional documented project contributors, and
  the data version history.
- Build orchestration, conversion, and packaging scripts in this repository are
  authored by repository contributors.

